4:FREEDOM MAKER my best tank I would say and its pretty nice lookin' DOWNLOAD LINK:https://kerbalx.com/___kerman/Freedom-maker

3:PZ IV F2 probably my favourite tank in the world DOWNLOAD LINK:https://kerbalx.com/___kerman/Pzkpfw-IV-ausf-F2

2:KW BALD EAGLE LINER my first ever jumbo jet and my first choice for traveling round kerbin DOWNLOAD LINK its on my spacecraft exchange;)

1:THE MALLARD to me its the nicest lookin' out of all of these and this is also on my spacecraft EXCHANGE
